HEADWORD: Nephrostome
<hw>Neph"ro*stome</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>nefro`s</grk> a kidney + <grk>sto`ma</grk> mouth.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool. & Anat.)</fld> <def>The funnel-shaped opening of a
nephridium into the body cavity.</def>⟦br⟧
